228
00:20:00,013 --> 00:20:02,766
I'll always remember this, Bender.

229
00:20:04,493 --> 00:20:06,927
Me too. Me too.

230
00:20:07,893 --> 00:20:08,928
Jerk.

231
00:20:11,533 --> 00:20:15,651
